  "title": "Senior Accountant",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Applications must be submitted through this portal to be considered. Any submissions made otherwise will be disqualified.</strong></h3><h3><strong></strong></h3><p><u>Full-sets of Accounting Management </u></p><p>The Senior Accountant is responsible for the day-to-day operations in accounting, applying accounting principles and procedures to analyze financial information, prepare accurate and timely financial reports and statements and ensure appropriate accounting control procedures.<br /><br /><u>JOB REQUIREMENTS</u></p><p>● Degree in Accounting or Finance or related qualifications<br />● Minimum 3 years of relevant experience<br />● Candidate with SAP experience will be advantageous<br />● Strong working knowledge of Microsoft Office Applications <br />● Meticulous, pro‐active with positive attitude<br />● Able to work independently and in a team environment</p>",
